{"tid":1918214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請停止吹奏雞丁 黃圈YouTuber高手紹需要大家訂閱CLS","createTime":"2020-03-10T03:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T06:39:23.000Z","uid":291448,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3afc111b265200d69bff2a3bab216a8fbafa8951","tid":1918214,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:04:52.000Z","msg":"呢位YouTuber真係唔係講笑 <br />\n早喺反送中初期就已經專門剪片笑鳩班黑警<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ubHTRvvQe6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FubHTRvvQe6U&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=79973107\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ubHTRvvQe6U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IHusyaqsDHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIHusyaqsDHo&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=a1bb87b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IHusyaqsDHo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DGHxbvEOWaU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDGHxbvEOWaU&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=0211e480\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DGHxbvEOWaU</a><br />\n與此同時亦都會整啲香港示威感動時刻<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hJK7wBVkk_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhJK7wBVkk_A&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=95dcde57\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hJK7wBVkk_A</a><br />\n之後亦整咗一啲建制派議員同埋藍絲嘅柒事<br />\n俾一D對政治唔係太了解嘅人知道班建制派有幾咁戇鳩<br />\n同埋D藍絲幾咁弱智<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pfRfLn2QMrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpfRfLn2QMrE&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=8694f82b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pfRfLn2QMrE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/crQRgvpedI8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcrQRgvpedI8&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=a9a5ca79\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/crQRgvpedI8</a><br />\n與此同時亦會整D幫香港做實事嘅政治人物同議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JGWmy9GEBrg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJGWmy9GEBrg&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=3d8ada30\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JGWmy9GEBrg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JGLU1KFf_6Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJGLU1KFf_6Q&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=1ccbb8cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JGLU1KFf_6Q</a><br />\n一個咁黃咁高質嘅YouTuber都剩係得差唔多三萬訂閱<br />\n實在太少啦 大家一齊幫手推佢上佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比更多人知道呢個咁高質嘅YouTuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢叫高手紹啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada503da84904b03fa4ef83340734f179eb89d82","tid":1918214,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d0d648ca575b2c891b76305643ada2648f5e66e","tid":1918214,"uid":291448,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:06:39.000Z","msg":"與其吹奏雞丁 倒不如吹奏自己黃圈手足 高手紹仲好過啦"},{"pid":"f51ada64295c0766a7a19d13d4464c276c4c60a0","tid":1918214,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"高手紹需要大家嘅支持啊 佢個頻道成日都比班藍絲搞<br />\n搞到好多片都比YouTube set咗做年齡限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a86d1b4884f7810db5ed560ad7fe620751c35b","tid":1918214,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"幫推